Code: ```8010 (0x1F4A)```
<!--Text-->
Text: ```"The transaction was aborted because of a failure to allocate file storage space."```

### Resolution
_There is currently no code example available on how to remedy error 8010. Please modify the code below in a way that can describe how to remedy this error._

```csharp
using Starcounter;
using System;

class Program {
    static void Main(string[] args) {
        // We call PreFoo() prior to calling Foo(). Now, we will
        // no longer experience error 8010.
        Db.PreFoo();
        Db.Foo();
    }
}
```
